<div dir="ltr"><div>In both trunk and 1.8.2rc3 the behavior is to enable oshmem by default.<br></div><div><br></div><div>In the 1.8.2rc3 tarball the configure help output matches the behavior.</div><div>HOWEVER, in the trunk the configure help output still says oshmem is DISabled by default.</div>
